-- London’s Oxford Street Closed as Police Examine Suspect Package
-- B y   S o f i a   H o r t a   e   C o s t a
-- 2012-08-16T15:36:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-16/london-s-oxford-street-closed-as-police-examine-suspect-package.html
Oxford Street in central  London  was
partially closed and evacuated as police investigate a
“suspicious package” in the area, said Rob Singh, a
Metropolitan Police Service spokesman.  He declined to comment on the likelihood of a controlled
explosion.  To contact the reporter on this story:
